org.w3.ldp.testsuite.reporter

Class LdpEarlReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.w3.ldp.testsuite.reporter.AbstractEarlReporter
      • org.w3.ldp.testsuite.reporter.LdpEarlReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.testng.IReporter, org.testng.ITestNGListener

    public class LdpEarlReporter
extends AbstractEarlReporter
implements org.testng.IReporter
    Earl Reporter for the LDP Test Suite. Takes in the results of the test suite and reports the information to a Turtle file and a JSON-LD file, both of which contains Earl vocabulary.
